swapi_c Documentation!¶

This Documentation about swapi_c. This program requests information from swapi.dev in JSON format and shows them using GUI.

Contents:

  • TakeJson – takes json file using httpie to make an API request for a resource.
  • JsonInf – reads information about some object in JSON file
  • swapi – creates GUI for swapi.dev using gtk+ 3
